sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Demo.ClientCredentials
    participant Auth as NexusAuth
    participant Api as Demo.Bff /api/m2m/profile

    Client->>Auth: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration
    Auth-->>Client: 返回 discovery

    Client->>Client: 使用本地私钥生成 client_assertion<br/>sub = iss = client_id<br/>aud = /connect/token<br/>alg = RS256<br/>包含 jti / exp / kid
    Client->>Auth: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=client_credentials<br/>scope=demo_api<br/>client_assertion(private_key_jwt)
    Auth->>Auth: 校验 client_assertion<br/>- 签名 / JWKS<br/>- iss == sub == client_id<br/>- aud == /connect/token<br/>- alg == RS256<br/>- jti 防重放
    Auth->>Auth: 校验 grant_type / scope / client resource 权限
    Auth-->>Client: access_token

    Client->>Api: GET /api/m2m/profile<br/>Authorization: Bearer access_token
    Api->>Auth: 使用资源服务器 JWT 校验配置验证 access_token
    Auth-->>Api: access_token 有效
    Api-->>Client: 返回机器客户端信息
